OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAnti-drone laser weapon hub
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto be created in Scotland  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A European hub for high-energy laser   
OL,6, weaponry is to be based in Livingston, 
OL,7, Scotland, a big defence firm has said. 
OL,9,FRaytheon UK said the "advanced laser   
OL,10,Fintegration centre" would open next    
OL,11,Fyear and would help meet growing demand
OL,12,Ffor laser weapons designed to destroy  
OL,13,Fsmall attack drones.                   
OL,15,FThe firm said the war in Ukraine had   
OL,16,Fhighlighted the threat they posed.     
OL,18,FThe centre will focus on the testing,  
OL,19,Ffielding and maintenance of defensive  
OL,20,Fhigh-energy laser (HEL) weapons.       
